i remember having this one mod that added propellers, and many cockpits, the one I remember specifically was one that resembled the TU-95, it also added the corresponding contra rotating turbo prop as well. It wasn’t airplanes plus, and it was for Ksp 1.8.1

i believe it also added An-225 parts, very very large Flaps and wings, and two turbofan engines.
